name: AJ Gregory
body:
Hello!

My name is AJ Gregory and I am seeking a position as a web developer.
I am a driven, hard working individual who is always eager to learn and
develop. My skills include Ruby, Rails, SQL, JavaScript, Backbone.js,
and Git.

## Projects

### Blog Jamboree!
A blogging app inspired by tumblr. Backbone.js with Rails back end.
https://github.com/aj-gregory/BlogJamboree

### ActiveRecord Lite
Active record clone, implements features of ActiveRecord such as querying,
mass assignment, and has_many and belongs_to associations.
https://github.com/aj-gregory/ActiveRecordLite
